  <brief_title>Extension Study to the Open-label, Multi-center, Expanded Access Study of Everolimus in Patients With Advanced Neuroendocrine Tumors</brief_title>
  <official_title>Extension Study to the Open-label, Multi-center, Expanded Access Study of Everolimus in Patients With Advanced Neuroendocrine Tumors</official_title>
